   <mods:abstract>Count Montfort, the bearer of this letter and formerly a major in Count
            Pulaski's Legion, desires to be employed in America. He has a plan of education which he
            will probably present, but Jay thinks that the time for such projects probably has not
            yet come. The Minister still delays. "I think that America will not have important if
            any aids from Spain."</mods:abstract>
